WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:00.000
Subtites By Rajanee

2
00:00:02.000 --> 00:00:08.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

3
00:00:50.000 --> 00:00:52.300
- Is it a girl?
- Yes.

4
00:00:52.500 --> 00:00:55.300
- Show me its arm.
- She bears the mark.

5
00:00:55.600 --> 00:00:57.600
No!

6
00:00:59.800 --> 00:01:03.300
The omen is true.
I must tell my mother.

7
00:01:05.800 --> 00:01:07.900
- Please help me!
- I can't.

8
00:01:08.200 --> 00:01:10.500
They're going to kill her.

9
00:01:14.900 --> 00:01:17.400
Please! Please!

10
00:01:20.100 --> 00:01:23.400
Oh. thank you. Ethna.
Thank you.

11
00:01:31.600 --> 00:01:34.000
Stand aside for Queen Bavmorda!

12
00:01:58.700 --> 00:02:00.800
You cannot stop the prophecy!

13
00:02:01.100 --> 00:02:04.000
This child will have no power over me.
Start the ritual.

14
00:02:04.200 --> 00:02:06.400
No. No!

15
00:02:06.700 --> 00:02:08.800
Where's the baby?

16
00:02:09.100 --> 00:02:11.400
- The midwife.
- Find that baby. Sorsha.

17
00:02:11.700 --> 00:02:14.800
Use the dogs.
Bring her back to me alive!

18
00:02:15.100 --> 00:02:17.100
Your reign of terror
is at an end!

19
00:02:17.300 --> 00:02:19.200
She will come back.
and she will finish you!

20
00:02:19.500 --> 00:02:22.800
- My baby will finish you!
- Kill her.

21
00:05:50.400 --> 00:05:52.300
Dada! Dada!

22
00:05:55.800 --> 00:05:57.800
- Dada! Dada!
- Whoa! Whoa!

23
00:06:00.400 --> 00:06:03.400
Dada! Dada!
We found something in the river.

24
00:06:03.600 --> 00:06:05.400
I can't run off and play
with you now. Ranon.

25
00:06:05.700 --> 00:06:07.700
- I've got work to do.
- You gotta come. Hurry!

26
00:06:13.500 --> 00:06:15.300
Come on.

27
00:06:18.200 --> 00:06:20.700
Don't go near it.
We don't know where it's been.

28
00:06:20.900 --> 00:06:23.600
But. Dada. it's a baby.

29
00:06:23.900 --> 00:06:28.400
- It's not like us.
- No. It's not a Nelwyn.

30
00:06:28.800 --> 00:06:32.100
- It looks like a Daikini baby.
- What's a Daikini?

31
00:06:32.400 --> 00:06:36.000
Daikinis are big.
Giants who live far away.

32
00:06:38.000 --> 00:06:40.200
She's so cute.

33
00:06:40.400 --> 00:06:43.200
- Can't we keep it. Dada?
- No!

34
00:06:44.900 --> 00:06:49.500
We'll push it downstream
and forget we ever saw it. Come on.

35
00:06:49.800 --> 00:06:51.600
Ufgood! Willow Ufgood!

36
00:06:52.900 --> 00:06:55.800
It's the prefect.
That's all I need.

37
00:06:56.000 --> 00:06:59.200
Keep it quiet.
Don't touch it.

38
00:07:01.000 --> 00:07:05.300
Mr Burglekutt. my husband
hasn't stolen anything!

39
00:07:10.800 --> 00:07:13.600
Ufgood. you still haven't paid
your debts to me.

40
00:07:13.900 --> 00:07:15.800
Where did you get these seeds?

41
00:07:16.100 --> 00:07:18.600
Well. maybe I used magic.

42
00:07:19.900 --> 00:07:22.600
You're no sorcerer. Ufgood.
You're a clown.

43
00:07:22.800 --> 00:07:26.200
I sell the planting seeds around here.
Now tell me where you got them.

44
00:07:26.500 --> 00:07:29.800
My family's been gathering them
in the forest since last fall.

45
00:07:30.000 --> 00:07:32.800
There's no law against that.
Mr Burglekutt.

46
00:07:33.200 --> 00:07:36.400
Willow. you didn't leave them
alone by the river?

47
00:07:38.300 --> 00:07:39.200
Magic?

48
00:07:39.400 --> 00:07:42.800
You'll need magic to get your planting
done before the rains start.

49
00:07:45.200 --> 00:07:47.000
I will have this land. Ufgood...

50
00:07:47.200 --> 00:07:50.500
and you're gonna end up
working in the mines.

51
00:08:01.100 --> 00:08:02.700
You're lovely.

52
00:08:02.900 --> 00:08:04.800
Yes. you are.

53
00:08:05.000 --> 00:08:06.400
Kiaya!

54
00:08:07.500 --> 00:08:09.300
Oh. Willow!

55
00:08:09.400 --> 00:08:10.500
Good girl.

56
00:08:10.700 --> 00:08:14.200
Absolutely.
under no condition whatsoever...

57
00:08:14.500 --> 00:08:17.100
is anyone in this family
to fall in love with that baby.

58
00:08:17.300 --> 00:08:21.800
Yes. you are. Come on. Mims.
Come on.

59
00:08:22.100 --> 00:08:24.000
There we are. Come on.

60
00:08:24.200 --> 00:08:26.900
Hey. I will not be ignored!

61
00:08:27.300 --> 00:08:29.500
Mims? Ranon?

62
00:08:42.100 --> 00:08:44.600
You're gonna be all clean.

63
00:08:51.100 --> 00:08:53.600
Willow. do you think we should
take her to the village council?

64
00:08:53.800 --> 00:08:56.200
No. No.
They'll think it's a bad omen.

65
00:08:56.500 --> 00:08:59.100
There'll be a flood or a drought.
and everyone will blame me for it.

66
00:08:59.400 --> 00:09:02.100
"Willow Ufgood brought around
that Daikini. didn't he?"

67
00:09:02.300 --> 00:09:05.100
"That's right. And he's that
lousy farmer too. Let's get him!"

68
00:09:05.400 --> 00:09:07.200
Willow. calm down.

69
00:09:07.400 --> 00:09:09.300
Calm down?

70
00:09:09.600 --> 00:09:11.500
Kiaya. tomorrow's my big day.

71
00:09:11.700 --> 00:09:15.200
Love. the High Aldwin hasn't picked
a new apprentice in years.

72
00:09:15.500 --> 00:09:18.600
Tomorrow's gonna be different.
I just know he's gonna pick me.

73
00:09:21.500 --> 00:09:25.000
- Here. Hold her.
- Hey. no. I don't want her. Kiaya.

74
00:09:25.300 --> 00:09:27.900
Hold her while I get some milk.

75
00:09:35.700 --> 00:09:38.100
Dada. she likes you.

76
00:09:47.800 --> 00:09:49.300
Bye.

77
00:09:50.900 --> 00:09:52.900
Come on. kids. Let's go.

78
00:10:00.500 --> 00:10:03.900
I will now magically join the rings!

79
00:10:33.100 --> 00:10:34.400
Thank you. son.

80
00:10:35.900 --> 00:10:39.400
If you're easily shocked.
please turn away.

81
00:10:56.100 --> 00:10:58.200
Give me a ripe one. Good.

82
00:11:04.600 --> 00:11:08.600
And now.
for my final amazing feat...

83
00:11:08.900 --> 00:11:13.000
I will make
this entire pig disappear!

84
00:11:23.800 --> 00:11:27.000
Please watch very closely.

85
00:11:27.200 --> 00:11:30.900
<i>Wuppity bairn. deru. deru!</i>

86
00:11:36.600 --> 00:11:38.600
What happened to your pig?

87
00:11:40.300 --> 00:11:43.100
No!
Hey. come here. you!

88
00:11:47.800 --> 00:11:49.700
I seen enough.

89
00:12:06.200 --> 00:12:07.500
Attention!

90
00:12:08.300 --> 00:12:12.300
The High Aldwin will now make his choice
for his new apprentice!

91
00:12:12.600 --> 00:12:15.900
Bring forth the hopefuls.

92
00:12:16.200 --> 00:12:18.400
- Good luck.
- Good luck. Dada.

93
00:12:18.700 --> 00:12:22.200
Willow Ufgood. a hopeful?
How did he get picked?

94
00:12:22.500 --> 00:12:24.800
Is this a joke?

95
00:12:32.900 --> 00:12:37.100
Magic is the bloodstream
of the universe!

96
00:12:37.900 --> 00:12:41.800
Forget all you know
or think you know.

97
00:12:42.100 --> 00:12:45.900
All that you require
is your intuition.

98
00:12:46.200 --> 00:12:50.100
Now. the power
to control the world...

99
00:12:50.500 --> 00:12:53.600
is in which finger?

100
00:13:37.800 --> 00:13:40.100
No apprentice this year!

101
00:14:01.800 --> 00:14:05.000
- Where's Mims?
- I don't know. She was right here!

102
00:14:05.300 --> 00:14:08.000
Take Ranon in there. quick!

103
00:14:16.100 --> 00:14:17.700
Mims!

104
00:14:36.900 --> 00:14:38.500
I'm scared. Dada!

105
00:14:50.300 --> 00:14:52.700
Come on!

106
00:15:10.500 --> 00:15:12.300
Vohnkar!

107
00:15:23.000 --> 00:15:25.700
- Check to make sure.
- It's dead!

108
00:15:28.200 --> 00:15:29.900
Dada! Dada!

109
00:15:33.300 --> 00:15:35.400
It was looking
for somebody's baby!

110
00:15:39.400 --> 00:15:42.200
- Mommy.
- Kiaya!

111
00:15:54.400 --> 00:15:56.100
I'm here.

112
00:16:04.200 --> 00:16:06.100
We can't keep the baby. Kiaya.

113
00:16:06.300 --> 00:16:09.000
We have to take her
to the village council.

114
00:16:22.500 --> 00:16:24.100
Silence!

115
00:16:24.300 --> 00:16:27.400
One beast we can kill.
but there may be more.

116
00:16:27.700 --> 00:16:29.800
And you can be assured
that they won't give up...

117
00:16:30.100 --> 00:16:32.000
until they find
what they're looking for!

118
00:16:32.100 --> 00:16:35.200
- It's a sign!
- Who's to blame for this?

119
00:16:35.500 --> 00:16:37.800
We must find the culprit
and throw him in the pit!

120
00:16:40.300 --> 00:16:42.800
In the pit! In the pit!

121
00:16:48.000 --> 00:16:49.900
Willow.

122
00:16:50.200 --> 00:16:51.600
Willow Ufgood.

123
00:16:53.900 --> 00:16:55.600
Come forward.

124
00:17:02.300 --> 00:17:06.400
My children found this baby
alone by the river. High Aldwin.

125
00:17:12.400 --> 00:17:14.300
A Daikini child.

126
00:17:14.600 --> 00:17:17.400
That's what the beasts want.
Let's give it back to them!

127
00:17:19.100 --> 00:17:22.200
- They'll kill her! You can't!
- It isn't one of us.

128
00:17:22.400 --> 00:17:24.900
This child is special!

129
00:17:25.900 --> 00:17:29.200
This child must be taken
beyond the boundaries of our village.

130
00:17:29.500 --> 00:17:32.400
All the way across
the great river...

131
00:17:32.600 --> 00:17:34.600
to the Daikini crossroads.

132
00:17:34.800 --> 00:17:37.100
Well. who'll do that?

133
00:17:37.800 --> 00:17:40.000
It seems only fair...

134
00:17:40.300 --> 00:17:42.600
that the man to take
this baby to the crossroads...

135
00:17:42.800 --> 00:17:45.700
be the very man
who plucked it out of the river.

136
00:17:47.600 --> 00:17:50.000
I nominate Willow Ufgood.

137
00:17:50.200 --> 00:17:51.300
No!

138
00:17:52.800 --> 00:17:55.100
I will consult the bones!

139
00:18:04.300 --> 00:18:07.200
The bones tell me nothing.

140
00:18:12.500 --> 00:18:14.600
Do you have any love
for this child?

141
00:18:23.600 --> 00:18:25.000
Yes.

142
00:18:26.300 --> 00:18:27.700
Yes. I do.

143
00:18:27.900 --> 00:18:30.800
The bones have spoken!

144
00:18:32.400 --> 00:18:36.100
Willow Ufgood. the safety
of this village depends upon you.

145
00:18:36.400 --> 00:18:40.200
- Praise the bones!
- Praise the bones!

146
00:18:40.600 --> 00:18:42.900
But you will need help.

147
00:18:43.100 --> 00:18:48.100
Who has the courage to protect
our brave fellow on his journey?

148
00:18:50.900 --> 00:18:54.400
- I'll go with him.
- Ah. Meegosh.

149
00:18:54.700 --> 00:18:56.100
Excellent choice.

150
00:18:56.900 --> 00:19:00.400
- I'll go!
- Vohnkar! Vohnkar!

151
00:19:00.600 --> 00:19:03.100
No! Not Vohnkar!
He's the best warrior in the village!

152
00:19:03.300 --> 00:19:06.300
We need him here!
Vohnkar. step back!

153
00:19:14.200 --> 00:19:17.000
All this expedition needs
is a leader.

154
00:19:18.600 --> 00:19:22.400
And according to the bones.
that leader is...

155
00:19:23.700 --> 00:19:25.500
you. Burglekutt!

156
00:19:27.400 --> 00:19:29.100
Vohnkar!

157
00:19:30.200 --> 00:19:34.100
- What's your problem. son?
- How do you mean?

158
00:19:35.000 --> 00:19:39.500
When I held up my fingers.
what was your first impulse?

159
00:19:39.800 --> 00:19:42.700
- Well. it was stupid.
- Just tell me.

160
00:19:43.800 --> 00:19:46.300
- To pick my own finger.
- Aha!

161
00:19:46.500 --> 00:19:49.900
That was the correct answer.
You lack faith in yourself.

162
00:19:50.200 --> 00:19:52.800
More than anyone in the village...

163
00:19:53.200 --> 00:19:55.600
you have the potential
to be a great sorcerer.

164
00:19:55.900 --> 00:20:00.400
Now. when you're out there.
listen to your own heart.

165
00:20:02.300 --> 00:20:04.600
These will protect you.

166
00:20:04.800 --> 00:20:07.400
- Acorns?
- They're magic!

167
00:20:07.800 --> 00:20:11.500
Anything you throw them at
turns to stone.

168
00:20:14.800 --> 00:20:17.900
You have much to learn.
young Ufgood.

169
00:20:30.900 --> 00:20:32.600
Are you scared. Dada?

170
00:20:34.300 --> 00:20:35.400
No.

171
00:20:35.500 --> 00:20:37.400
Even with fairies in the woods...

172
00:20:37.700 --> 00:20:39.500
that'll put you to sleep
for a hundred years?

173
00:20:41.200 --> 00:20:43.600
- Doesn't bother me.
- Brownies?

174
00:20:43.900 --> 00:20:46.600
- Dragons?
- Trolls?

175
00:20:47.000 --> 00:20:50.200
Trolls that'll skin you alive
and take your face off?

176
00:20:50.500 --> 00:20:53.800
Ranon!
You know I hate trolls.

177
00:20:54.200 --> 00:20:56.500
I can be your guard
and carry your spear.

178
00:20:56.800 --> 00:20:58.900
Me too. Me too. Dada.

179
00:21:00.500 --> 00:21:02.700
What a lucky father I am.

180
00:21:03.000 --> 00:21:05.600
I wish I could take
you bobbins with me.

181
00:21:09.000 --> 00:21:11.000
Goodbye. Dada.

182
00:21:13.700 --> 00:21:15.800
Go play! Go on.

183
00:21:21.400 --> 00:21:24.100
We've never been apart.

184
00:21:27.000 --> 00:21:29.200
I miss you already.

185
00:21:30.200 --> 00:21:31.900
Don't worry. Kiaya.

186
00:21:32.200 --> 00:21:35.900
I'll be fine. and I'll be back
before you know it.

187
00:21:38.500 --> 00:21:41.000
Well. remember to keep her warm.

188
00:21:43.200 --> 00:21:45.700
And here.

189
00:21:48.100 --> 00:21:50.700
This will bring you luck.

190
00:22:04.800 --> 00:22:07.200
Good brave people!

191
00:22:08.200 --> 00:22:10.800
The outer world is
no place for a Nelwyn.

192
00:22:11.000 --> 00:22:13.500
Give the baby
to the first Daikini you see...

193
00:22:13.700 --> 00:22:15.800
then hurry home.

194
00:22:19.300 --> 00:22:22.700
<i>Tuatha lawkathok tuatha!</i>

195
00:22:23.700 --> 00:22:26.200
Go in the direction
the bird is flying!

196
00:22:31.100 --> 00:22:33.100
It's going back to the village!

197
00:22:35.000 --> 00:22:37.100
Ignore the bird.
Follow the river.

198
00:22:37.300 --> 00:22:39.200
Move out!

199
00:23:03.500 --> 00:23:06.300
- Hold on. Meegosh.
- What's wrong?

200
00:23:07.000 --> 00:23:09.100
We have to stop.

201
00:23:09.400 --> 00:23:10.900
Stop? Why?

202
00:23:11.100 --> 00:23:13.400
The baby's sick.

203
00:23:18.200 --> 00:23:20.600
She's not sick!
Let me see.

204
00:23:24.600 --> 00:23:26.600
Take her! Take her!

205
00:23:28.100 --> 00:23:30.900
She'll be fine
once she gets some rest.

206
00:23:34.400 --> 00:23:35.900
Clean me up.

207
00:23:39.300 --> 00:23:41.800
I didn't ask you
to bring me a dead nursemaid.

208
00:23:42.100 --> 00:23:45.400
- Sorsha. you're useless!
- I'm backtracking the nursemaid's trail.

209
00:23:45.700 --> 00:23:48.100
I'll find where she hid the baby.

210
00:23:50.300 --> 00:23:52.400
Ah. General Kael. at last.

211
00:23:53.400 --> 00:23:57.100
My queen. I have destroyed
the castle at Galladoorn.

212
00:23:57.400 --> 00:24:00.900
Well done. But now I have
another task for you.

213
00:24:01.100 --> 00:24:06.300
Help my daughter to find
that tiny. helpless baby...

214
00:24:06.600 --> 00:24:08.400
that continues somehow
to elude her.

215
00:24:10.600 --> 00:24:13.500
The baby of the prophecy?
The one that would destroy you?

216
00:24:13.800 --> 00:24:15.900
I need that baby alive.

217
00:24:16.100 --> 00:24:18.400
I must perform
the ritual that will exile...

218
00:24:18.600 --> 00:24:21.800
the child's spirit into oblivion.

219
00:24:22.100 --> 00:24:24.700
- Find her!
- I don't need his help. Mother.

220
00:24:24.900 --> 00:24:26.800
You'll do as I say. child.

221
00:24:33.400 --> 00:24:35.400
I read the signs.

222
00:24:35.600 --> 00:24:38.600
One day. I fear.
your daughter will betray you.

223
00:24:38.900 --> 00:24:42.900
I trust her loyalty
more than I trust yours.

224
00:24:59.300 --> 00:25:01.000
Move!

225
00:25:01.800 --> 00:25:04.700
It's an ambush.
Come on. Move!

226
00:25:07.600 --> 00:25:09.200
Come on!

227
00:25:21.000 --> 00:25:22.800
The Nelwyns have got the baby.

228
00:25:23.000 --> 00:25:25.600
We've searched the village. but a group
of them are on the road somewhere.

229
00:25:25.800 --> 00:25:28.700
They couldn't have gone far!

230
00:25:28.900 --> 00:25:31.000
Widen the search
and report to Sorsha!

231
00:25:39.300 --> 00:25:41.300
Come.
We'll keep to the woods.

232
00:26:21.100 --> 00:26:22.500
That's it!

233
00:26:22.600 --> 00:26:24.600
It's the crossroads!

234
00:26:42.100 --> 00:26:45.200
Keep this fire high.
We don't know what's out there.

235
00:26:51.400 --> 00:26:53.500
What was that?

236
00:26:54.700 --> 00:26:56.300
Get the spears!

237
00:27:15.100 --> 00:27:18.600
Give me some water. peck.
or you die.

238
00:27:18.900 --> 00:27:21.100
Do you understand?

239
00:27:21.400 --> 00:27:23.100
Water.

240
00:27:25.900 --> 00:27:27.200
Hurry up!

241
00:27:31.400 --> 00:27:34.100
Get me some water.
you measly little pecks!

242
00:27:35.700 --> 00:27:37.700
It's a Daikini. We're in luck.

243
00:27:38.900 --> 00:27:41.800
- We can't give her to him!
- Somebody put him there for a reason.

244
00:27:42.200 --> 00:27:46.200
Ufgood. we've got to get rid of her.
Those soldiers are after us.

245
00:27:47.200 --> 00:27:49.800
He's looking right at us.

246
00:27:53.900 --> 00:27:55.800
We've got to give
that baby to somebody.

247
00:27:56.700 --> 00:27:58.700
I'm somebody.

248
00:27:59.600 --> 00:28:02.500
Let me out of here.
I'll take care of the baby.

249
00:28:05.100 --> 00:28:07.300
I trust him completely.

250
00:28:07.600 --> 00:28:11.100
- But he tried to strangle me!
- I want to go home.

251
00:28:11.500 --> 00:28:14.900
No. Burglekutt!
We should wait!

252
00:28:15.100 --> 00:28:17.000
Are you challenging my authority?

253
00:28:17.200 --> 00:28:20.400
As far as this baby
is concerned. yes.

254
00:28:20.700 --> 00:28:23.600
Don't listen to him. Burglekutt.

255
00:28:24.900 --> 00:28:28.600
Fine. You stay here alone.
but we're going.

256
00:28:30.100 --> 00:28:32.700
That's a bad idea. Very bad.
Dangerous out there.

257
00:28:33.100 --> 00:28:36.900
- Get the gear. men.
- Vohnkar...

258
00:28:37.100 --> 00:28:42.000
- It's not his decision!
- Burglekutt. you're troll dung.

259
00:28:42.400 --> 00:28:46.000
- Don't let him talk to you that way.
- Listen here. runt.

260
00:28:46.300 --> 00:28:49.900
While you're wasting your time here.
your fields aren't getting planted.

261
00:28:50.200 --> 00:28:52.000
Think about it!

262
00:28:52.100 --> 00:28:56.100
- Burglekutt. I'm gonna...
- You're gonna what?

263
00:29:01.700 --> 00:29:04.400
Someday. Burglekutt.
Someday.

264
00:29:04.700 --> 00:29:06.500
Vohnkar. let's go!

265
00:29:10.200 --> 00:29:12.900
Meegosh. are you coming?

266
00:29:15.400 --> 00:29:16.900
I'm staying.

267
00:29:17.100 --> 00:29:18.800
Come on. men.

268
00:29:19.000 --> 00:29:22.900
Burglekutt. let me out of here.
I'll take care of the baby. I swear.

269
00:29:23.900 --> 00:29:25.900
Just let me out of here.
Please!

270
00:29:26.100 --> 00:29:29.300
Vohnkar. let me borrow that spear
just for a minute.

271
00:29:29.600 --> 00:29:31.700
Well. at least get me some water!

272
00:29:31.900 --> 00:29:34.700
Burglekutt. don't leave me alone
with these two!

273
00:29:39.400 --> 00:29:41.600
What'll we do now. Willow?

274
00:29:41.800 --> 00:29:44.300
Well. that was really stupid. peck.

275
00:29:44.500 --> 00:29:49.100
- Don't call me a peck.
- Oh. I'm sorry. peck.

276
00:29:49.400 --> 00:29:52.900
- Peck. peck. peck. peck.
- You be careful!

277
00:29:54.000 --> 00:29:56.700
I'm a powerful sorcerer.
See this acorn?

278
00:29:58.400 --> 00:30:01.000
I'll throw it at you
and turn you to stone.

279
00:30:02.900 --> 00:30:04.700
I'm really scared.

280
00:30:05.000 --> 00:30:07.300
No. don't! Don't!

281
00:30:07.600 --> 00:30:10.500
There's a peck here
with an acorn pointed at me!

282
00:30:11.600 --> 00:30:13.400
I wouldn't want to waste it!

283
00:30:15.500 --> 00:30:19.300
Peck. peck. peck. peck!

284
00:30:48.800 --> 00:30:50.700
What was that?

285
00:30:54.300 --> 00:30:56.700
Mornin'. boys.

286
00:30:58.100 --> 00:31:01.100
Rough night last night.
wasn't it?

287
00:31:02.400 --> 00:31:05.500
I don't think
I introduced myself yesterday.

288
00:31:05.700 --> 00:31:09.000
My name is Madmartigan.
and you are. uh...

289
00:31:09.300 --> 00:31:11.300
No. Meegosh.

290
00:31:11.400 --> 00:31:13.600
Don't go near him.
He's dangerous.

291
00:31:13.800 --> 00:31:15.600
I am not.

292
00:31:16.900 --> 00:31:18.900
Good.

293
00:31:22.700 --> 00:31:24.800
Stop! Wait!

294
00:31:35.700 --> 00:31:38.300
- What's going on?
- Smells like a battle.

295
00:31:40.100 --> 00:31:42.000
I suppose you're a warrior.

296
00:31:42.200 --> 00:31:44.500
I am the greatest swordsman
that ever lived.

297
00:31:47.600 --> 00:31:51.100
Say. could I have
some of that water?

298
00:32:01.200 --> 00:32:03.300
I don't know why I try.

299
00:32:11.200 --> 00:32:13.800
I guess I am gonna die here.
Who cares?

300
00:32:14.000 --> 00:32:15.800
- Here.
- Thanks. friend.

301
00:32:17.700 --> 00:32:19.500
What's that?

302
00:32:19.700 --> 00:32:22.200
I'd say
two or three hundred horses...

303
00:32:22.600 --> 00:32:26.300
five or six wagons.
and about a thousand fools.

304
00:32:30.600 --> 00:32:32.900
- Thank you.
- Come on. Meegosh.

305
00:32:38.700 --> 00:32:40.900
It's gonna be all right.
little bobbin.

306
00:32:49.000 --> 00:32:50.800
Everything's gonna be all right.

307
00:32:54.400 --> 00:32:57.200
- Excuse me. sir.
- Out of the way. peck!

308
00:33:00.400 --> 00:33:02.300
Pardon me.

309
00:33:09.600 --> 00:33:11.200
Excuse me. sir.

310
00:33:12.500 --> 00:33:14.600
We found one of your babies
in our village.

311
00:33:14.800 --> 00:33:17.500
Will you please take care of her?

312
00:33:18.800 --> 00:33:22.000
We're going into battle. little ones.
Find a woman to take care of her.

313
00:33:23.300 --> 00:33:25.600
They thought you were
a woman. Airk.

314
00:33:26.900 --> 00:33:29.100
Well...

315
00:33:29.400 --> 00:33:31.700
Madmartigan!
What did you do this time?

316
00:33:32.000 --> 00:33:33.800
Nothing you wouldn't have done
in my place.

317
00:33:34.000 --> 00:33:36.400
I always knew
you'd end up in a crow's cage.

318
00:33:36.700 --> 00:33:39.700
At least I'm not herding sheep.
What are you doing this far north?

319
00:33:39.900 --> 00:33:42.700
The Nockmaar army
destroyed Galladoorn.

320
00:33:43.000 --> 00:33:44.600
The castle?

321
00:33:44.700 --> 00:33:46.600
Bavmorda's troops are crushing
everything in sight.

322
00:33:46.900 --> 00:33:48.600
Come on.
Let me out of here. Airk.

323
00:33:48.900 --> 00:33:50.900
Give me a sword.
I'll win this war for you.

324
00:33:51.200 --> 00:33:55.400
Madmartigan.
I still serve Galladoorn.

325
00:33:55.700 --> 00:33:57.500
You serve no one.

326
00:33:57.800 --> 00:33:59.900
Remember?

327
00:34:00.100 --> 00:34:02.000
Sit in your coffin and rot.

328
00:34:03.400 --> 00:34:06.200
Wait. Airk. You need me!

329
00:34:06.500 --> 00:34:08.700
I'll be around
long after you're dead!

330
00:34:09.000 --> 00:34:11.400
When I get out of here.
I'm gonna cut your head off...

331
00:34:11.700 --> 00:34:13.600
and stick it on a pig pole!

332
00:34:33.300 --> 00:34:35.700
I miss Kiaya and the bobbins.

333
00:34:40.400 --> 00:34:42.300
We're running out of food.

334
00:34:45.300 --> 00:34:47.400
Nobody's gonna
take care of that baby.

335
00:34:47.600 --> 00:34:50.300
You know why?
Nobody cares.

336
00:34:53.400 --> 00:34:55.400
Except me.

337
00:34:56.700 --> 00:35:01.100
You want to go back to your families.
I want out of this cage.

338
00:35:01.400 --> 00:35:05.100
Let me take care of that baby.
I'll look after her like she was my own.

339
00:35:05.400 --> 00:35:08.200
I believe he would. Willow.

340
00:35:08.500 --> 00:35:10.900
He doesn't know anything
about babies.

341
00:35:12.000 --> 00:35:16.100
Right. but I know
a lot of women who do.

342
00:35:17.200 --> 00:35:19.100
If I had somebody in my life...

343
00:35:20.200 --> 00:35:22.800
a little daughter. perhaps...

344
00:35:23.100 --> 00:35:26.100
I might have a reason
to go on living.

345
00:35:29.500 --> 00:35:32.500
You can't leave me
in here to die.

346
00:35:32.900 --> 00:35:35.400
Not when all I want to do
is protect her.

347
00:35:48.800 --> 00:35:52.500
I feel better!

348
00:35:52.800 --> 00:35:56.300
- You've done the right thing!
- Okay. All right.

349
00:35:56.600 --> 00:35:58.400
You gotta promise to feed her.

350
00:35:58.600 --> 00:36:00.900
Come to Daddy. little darlin'.

351
00:36:01.100 --> 00:36:04.100
- And keep her clean.
- Absolutely.

352
00:36:14.700 --> 00:36:16.500
She likes me.

353
00:36:18.600 --> 00:36:20.800
Here are her changing rags.

354
00:36:21.100 --> 00:36:23.100
- And her milk bladder.
- Any milk in there?

355
00:36:23.400 --> 00:36:27.300
- It's for her!
- I wouldn't steal from a baby.

356
00:36:30.500 --> 00:36:32.700
You worry too much. peck.

357
00:36:33.000 --> 00:36:36.000
- It's Willow.
- I mean Willow.

358
00:36:37.500 --> 00:36:40.300
Now listen. boys... Willow.

359
00:36:40.500 --> 00:36:42.600
You've done the right thing.

360
00:36:42.800 --> 00:36:45.900
Now I want you to get home
and bring your crop in.

361
00:36:52.300 --> 00:36:54.500
Goodbye. little one.

362
00:37:05.800 --> 00:37:07.800
Please take good care of her.

363
00:37:10.200 --> 00:37:12.300
I give you my word of honour!

364
00:37:19.800 --> 00:37:22.900
- Meegosh. slow down!
- Oh. come on!

365
00:37:23.300 --> 00:37:25.600
If we hurry. we could be home
by tomorrow morning.

366
00:37:25.900 --> 00:37:28.400
We'll be heroes.

367
00:37:28.600 --> 00:37:30.900
- Do you really think so?
- Sure.

368
00:37:31.100 --> 00:37:33.200
"Look. there's Willow and Meegosh.

369
00:37:33.500 --> 00:37:35.600
The heroes have come home."

370
00:37:35.800 --> 00:37:38.700
"Welcome back. boys.
You deserve medals!"

371
00:37:38.900 --> 00:37:41.100
Yeah. medals!

372
00:37:48.900 --> 00:37:51.200
Did we do the right thing?

373
00:37:51.500 --> 00:37:54.200
Absolutely.
There's nothing to worry about.

374
00:38:02.800 --> 00:38:07.700
I stole the baby! I stole the baby!

375
00:38:10.500 --> 00:38:13.600
That's my baby!
Stop! Wait! Come back!

376
00:38:13.900 --> 00:38:16.800
Left. you stupid bird. Left!

377
00:38:23.600 --> 00:38:25.800
Brownies!
Let's get out of here!

378
00:38:27.000 --> 00:38:30.100
Come on. Meegosh!

379
00:38:36.400 --> 00:38:38.300
We'll outrun 'em!

380
00:38:43.100 --> 00:38:45.100
Hey. ugly. wake up!

381
00:38:52.800 --> 00:38:54.900
Stand your ground.
These are our prisoners.

382
00:38:55.100 --> 00:38:57.800
Meegosh. where's the baby?

383
00:38:58.100 --> 00:39:01.100
<i>- Bring the Nelwyns to me.</i>
- All right. you heard her!

384
00:39:01.400 --> 00:39:04.900
- What's going on?
- Shut up. or I'll break your nose.

385
00:39:05.100 --> 00:39:07.400
You are mine to toy with.

386
00:39:08.600 --> 00:39:11.000
Forward!

387
00:39:12.200 --> 00:39:14.000
Get the rope.

388
00:39:16.600 --> 00:39:21.200
Where did you get that baby?

389
00:39:21.500 --> 00:39:24.900
I stole it from a stupid Daikini.

390
00:39:27.700 --> 00:39:32.100
<i>Franjean. release the Nelwyns.</i>
<i>and stop pestering them.</i>

391
00:39:49.100 --> 00:39:51.000
<i>Welcome to my kingdom.</i>

392
00:39:59.200 --> 00:40:03.500
- I'm happy to meet you. Willow Ufgood.
- How do you know my name?

393
00:40:04.400 --> 00:40:06.900
Elora Danan told me.

394
00:40:07.100 --> 00:40:10.100
Elora?
Elora. Willow is here.

395
00:40:14.100 --> 00:40:18.500
- But she's just a baby.
- She's very special.

396
00:40:18.800 --> 00:40:23.100
My Brownies have been searching for her
ever since we heard she was born.

397
00:40:25.000 --> 00:40:28.900
Elora Danan has chosen you
to be her guardian.

398
00:40:29.200 --> 00:40:30.600
Me?

399
00:40:30.900 --> 00:40:34.100
Yes. She likes you.

400
00:40:35.400 --> 00:40:40.100
And Elora Danan knows
you have the courage to help us.

401
00:40:40.400 --> 00:40:43.800
Take my wand
to the sorceress Fin Raziel.

402
00:40:44.100 --> 00:40:48.100
She will guide you and Elora Danan
to the kingdom of Tir Asleen...

403
00:40:48.500 --> 00:40:51.400
where a good king and queen
will look after her.

404
00:40:51.600 --> 00:40:55.100
You need a warrior
for a job like this. I'm a nobody.

405
00:40:55.500 --> 00:40:58.600
Elora. you don't want me.

406
00:40:58.900 --> 00:41:02.300
Tell her.
I'm short. even for a Nelwyn.

407
00:41:06.800 --> 00:41:08.700
Hello?

408
00:41:15.500 --> 00:41:18.700
Elora Danan must survive!

409
00:41:19.000 --> 00:41:20.900
She must fulfil her destiny...

410
00:41:21.100 --> 00:41:23.700
and bring about the downfall
of Queen Bavmorda...

411
00:41:23.900 --> 00:41:26.500
whose powers are growing
like an evil plague.

412
00:41:26.800 --> 00:41:30.900
Unless she is stopped.
Bavmorda will control the lives...

413
00:41:31.300 --> 00:41:35.200
of your village.
your children... everyone.

414
00:41:40.500 --> 00:41:43.800
All creatures of good heart
need your help. Willow.

415
00:41:45.300 --> 00:41:47.700
The choice is yours.

416
00:42:12.400 --> 00:42:15.500
Hey. Meegosh. Wake up.

417
00:42:16.600 --> 00:42:19.500
- It's time to go home.
- Home?

418
00:42:23.700 --> 00:42:25.600
Listen. Meegosh.

419
00:42:25.900 --> 00:42:29.200
Tell Kiaya I love her
and I think of her every day.

420
00:42:31.900 --> 00:42:34.500
And tell her I'm not going to let
anything happen to the baby.

421
00:42:34.800 --> 00:42:37.200
Are you sure you know
what you're doing?

422
00:42:38.800 --> 00:42:40.300
I hope so.

423
00:42:41.900 --> 00:42:43.900
Listen. be careful.

424
00:42:51.000 --> 00:42:54.400
- I know the way. Franjean.
- You always think you know the way.

425
00:42:54.600 --> 00:42:56.400
I am the leader!

426
00:42:56.600 --> 00:42:59.100
- How long will it take to find Raziel?
- Not long.

427
00:42:59.300 --> 00:43:02.500
She's been exiled to an island
just over those hills.

428
00:43:02.900 --> 00:43:05.600
- She's what?
- Exiled.

429
00:43:05.800 --> 00:43:08.800
By the evil Queen Bavmorda.

430
00:43:10.000 --> 00:43:12.500
Rool. you fool. He does not need
to know everything!

431
00:43:12.700 --> 00:43:15.200
- I didn't tell him everything.
- You told him enough.

432
00:43:15.400 --> 00:43:18.500
You mentioned the island.
you mentioned the queen.

433
00:43:19.000 --> 00:43:20.200
So?

434
00:43:20.500 --> 00:43:23.100
What do you mean? What are
you saying. mysterious island?

435
00:43:23.300 --> 00:43:25.800
Don't play with that wand.

436
00:43:26.000 --> 00:43:28.400
Cherlindrea told you
it holds vast powers.

437
00:43:28.700 --> 00:43:33.700
Only a great sorcerer can use it.
not a stupid peck like you.

438
00:43:34.100 --> 00:43:37.100
- This way.
- No. No. No. I don't think so.

439
00:43:37.300 --> 00:43:39.400
- All right. then this way.
- Nope.

440
00:43:39.700 --> 00:43:42.100
- This way.
- This way?

441
00:43:42.300 --> 00:43:45.800
- That's what I said.
- This way.

442
00:43:46.100 --> 00:43:48.000
Are you sure you know
where you're going?

443
00:43:48.100 --> 00:43:52.000
Of course. With us as your guides.
no harm will befall you.

444
00:44:09.100 --> 00:44:11.000
We are not going in there!

445
00:44:11.200 --> 00:44:14.000
But Elora needs fresh milk.
and we're drenched.

446
00:44:14.200 --> 00:44:17.400
You are not in command
here. shorty. I am!

447
00:44:17.600 --> 00:44:19.600
You hear me?

448
00:44:59.000 --> 00:45:01.300
Excuse me? Excuse me.

449
00:45:01.500 --> 00:45:04.300
Could you spare some milk
for this poor. hungry baby?

450
00:45:04.600 --> 00:45:06.300
Get out of here. peck!

451
00:45:06.500 --> 00:45:09.100
Get outta here or we'll cook ya!

452
00:45:23.900 --> 00:45:26.000
Look at her!

453
00:45:26.300 --> 00:45:28.400
I could use a love potion on her!

454
00:45:28.500 --> 00:45:32.100
Franjean! Give me
that dust of broken heart.

455
00:45:32.500 --> 00:45:34.100
Come on! Give it to me!

456
00:45:34.300 --> 00:45:37.400
It's very dangerous.
It belongs to the fairies!

457
00:45:41.700 --> 00:45:43.700
Hey. quiet!
You want to get us killed?

458
00:45:50.800 --> 00:45:55.300
Oh. Rool! Always playing
with those fairy love potions.

459
00:45:59.200 --> 00:46:01.400
You are so beautiful!

460
00:46:03.200 --> 00:46:05.600
Your eyes!
Your whiskers!

461
00:46:05.800 --> 00:46:10.000
- I have to kiss you!
- Rool! That dust of broken heart!

462
00:46:25.200 --> 00:46:26.900
Beer!

463
00:46:30.400 --> 00:46:32.400
These people are crazy!
This could be bad!

464
00:46:37.100 --> 00:46:40.900
Hurry! Hurry!
My husband's coming!

465
00:46:41.100 --> 00:46:43.000
If he catches you here.
he'll kill us both!

466
00:46:43.300 --> 00:46:45.700
- How do I look?
- Not you!

467
00:46:47.100 --> 00:46:48.900
Where the hell did you come from?

468
00:46:49.100 --> 00:46:51.200
I knew I shouldn't
have trusted you.

469
00:46:51.400 --> 00:46:52.800
Don't I know you?

470
00:46:53.100 --> 00:46:56.500
I stole the baby from you. Daikini.
while you were taking a pee-pee!

471
00:46:56.900 --> 00:46:59.800
- Cover your face!
- You are crawling with Brownies.

472
00:47:00.200 --> 00:47:02.600
I hate Brownies!

473
00:47:04.500 --> 00:47:06.700
- Where is he?
- Hello. dear.

474
00:47:06.900 --> 00:47:09.100
There's nobody here
but me and. uh. my...

475
00:47:09.400 --> 00:47:11.600
- I'll kill him!
- My cousin. Hilda.

476
00:47:11.800 --> 00:47:13.900
Hilda?

477
00:47:14.200 --> 00:47:16.700
Hilda. this is my husband. Llug.

478
00:47:17.000 --> 00:47:19.000
Big husband.
How do you do?

479
00:47:23.600 --> 00:47:27.500
- Come on. girly. Don't be shy.
- Give her back!

480
00:47:28.500 --> 00:47:30.700
- Pecks make such terrible nursemaids.
- Nursemaid?

481
00:47:30.900 --> 00:47:32.900
They get too excited.

482
00:47:33.900 --> 00:47:36.300
Excuse me!
Are we having a party?

483
00:47:40.200 --> 00:47:41.900
Stop. please.

484
00:47:43.400 --> 00:47:46.300
Come on.
Fight like a man!

485
00:47:46.500 --> 00:47:48.200
Want to breed?

486
00:47:48.500 --> 00:47:51.300
Tempting. but no.

487
00:47:54.800 --> 00:47:57.200
- Thank you. Time to leave.
- Bye. Hilda!

488
00:47:57.500 --> 00:47:59.400
Take them out!

489
00:48:00.800 --> 00:48:04.000
Come along! Move along!

490
00:48:04.300 --> 00:48:06.800
Gather up all these babies.

491
00:48:07.100 --> 00:48:09.200
That baby over there.
Let me see its arm.

492
00:48:13.100 --> 00:48:15.100
That's not the one.

493
00:48:18.900 --> 00:48:21.500
You! Are you the mother
of that child?

494
00:48:21.700 --> 00:48:24.200
- Yes. I am.
- Let me see it.

495
00:48:24.500 --> 00:48:26.000
No! Don't let her!

496
00:48:27.700 --> 00:48:30.300
I gave you an order. woman!

497
00:48:41.700 --> 00:48:43.300
You're beautiful!

498
00:48:43.400 --> 00:48:46.500
- And you're very strong.
- Thank you.

499
00:48:49.700 --> 00:48:52.600
You're no woman!

500
00:48:52.900 --> 00:48:54.600
- Not a woman?
- Gentlemen...

501
00:48:54.900 --> 00:48:56.600
Not a woman?

502
00:48:56.800 --> 00:48:58.400
Meet Llug.

503
00:49:00.800 --> 00:49:02.700
- After them!
- Out of the way!

504
00:49:09.200 --> 00:49:10.300
To the horses!

505
00:49:22.900 --> 00:49:26.600
Madmartigan!
Madmartigan! Wait!

506
00:49:30.400 --> 00:49:32.700
He's not a woman!

507
00:49:39.300 --> 00:49:42.600
Madmartigan. stop!

508
00:50:01.700 --> 00:50:04.100
Madmartigan. I'm warning you...

509
00:50:07.600 --> 00:50:09.800
Prepare to die!

510
00:50:33.300 --> 00:50:35.500
Madmartigan! Stop!

511
00:50:51.700 --> 00:50:54.700
No more beer.

512
00:51:05.800 --> 00:51:07.700
Franjean. help me!

513
00:51:12.400 --> 00:51:15.200
- Rool! Rool!
- Help!

514
00:51:19.000 --> 00:51:22.300
- Rool! What are you doing?
- Help me!

515
00:51:27.900 --> 00:51:30.000
- Come on.
- Pull me in.

516
00:52:07.200 --> 00:52:10.600
Rool. this isn't funny!
Help me cut the rope!

517
00:52:48.300 --> 00:52:50.700
Willow. stay down!

518
00:52:54.500 --> 00:52:56.400
Whoa!

519
00:52:59.000 --> 00:53:00.700
Have you gone crazy?

520
00:53:01.000 --> 00:53:02.900
You can't chase around
with Elora like this.

521
00:53:03.200 --> 00:53:05.400
We're getting off!

522
00:53:39.100 --> 00:53:41.600
Now we stop. peck.

523
00:53:42.900 --> 00:53:45.300
Stupid Daikini!

524
00:53:45.500 --> 00:53:48.100
Ask him to stop the wagon.

525
00:53:48.300 --> 00:53:52.200
Madmartigan! You never. ever
drive that fast with an infant!

526
00:53:54.300 --> 00:53:56.400
I just saved that infant's life!

527
00:54:00.400 --> 00:54:02.200
Gather your wits. Come on.

528
00:54:02.400 --> 00:54:05.200
- Don't worry about me. I'm fine!
- Come on!

529
00:54:07.400 --> 00:54:08.600
Get down!

530
00:54:08.800 --> 00:54:11.000
Where am I?

531
00:54:13.000 --> 00:54:15.000
Rool. you fool.
get out of the road!

532
00:54:32.800 --> 00:54:35.500
You better clear out. Willow.
before those troops come back.

533
00:54:35.900 --> 00:54:39.100
- My head!
- We don't need him. Elora.

534
00:54:47.600 --> 00:54:49.600
Madmartigan. wait!

535
00:54:49.800 --> 00:54:52.900
Go home. Willow!
It's a dangerous world.

536
00:54:53.300 --> 00:54:55.100
Yeah. and that's why
we need your help.

537
00:54:55.300 --> 00:54:58.400
My help?
What do you need my help for?

538
00:54:58.600 --> 00:55:00.600
You're a sorcerer!

539
00:55:00.800 --> 00:55:03.900
You're a great warrior
and a swordsman.

540
00:55:04.100 --> 00:55:06.800
And you're ten times
bigger than I am. stupid!

541
00:55:08.200 --> 00:55:11.200
Are you trying to make my life
more difficult than it already is?

542
00:55:15.900 --> 00:55:18.400
Hurry! Big dogs!

543
00:55:18.600 --> 00:55:22.600
Look. I'm sorry I got angry.

544
00:55:22.900 --> 00:55:24.700
We wouldn't have escaped
without you.

545
00:55:39.000 --> 00:55:41.700
Well. don't expect me
to help you again.

546
00:55:43.400 --> 00:55:46.800
Good! Then we go that way!
To the lake!

547
00:55:49.100 --> 00:55:51.400
That way.

548
00:55:51.600 --> 00:55:54.700
You are drunk. and when
you are drunk. you forget that...

549
00:55:55.000 --> 00:55:56.800
- I am in charge!
- You are in charge.

550
00:55:57.000 --> 00:55:59.100
Fine.
Then which way do we go?

551
00:56:00.500 --> 00:56:02.700
That way!

552
00:56:04.300 --> 00:56:08.600
Oh. no!
That's the way I'm going.

553
00:56:09.000 --> 00:56:11.800
All right. all right.
You can follow me as far as the lake.

554
00:56:12.000 --> 00:56:14.000
But that's it!

555
00:56:14.300 --> 00:56:17.800
- You're not going south. are you?
- No. just as far as the lake.

556
00:56:18.200 --> 00:56:19.400
Good.

557
00:56:19.600 --> 00:56:23.000
Mumbo. Jumbo. I am hungry.
Go get me some eggs or something.

558
00:56:23.400 --> 00:56:25.800
- We are not afraid of you!
- Now!

559
00:56:32.600 --> 00:56:36.000
Kael. have you found the child?

560
00:56:37.400 --> 00:56:40.000
The search goes on. my queen.

561
00:56:40.300 --> 00:56:42.200
Why. with my powers...

562
00:56:42.300 --> 00:56:45.300
with the strength
of my great army...

563
00:56:45.700 --> 00:56:48.900
can you not find
one little child?

564
00:56:49.100 --> 00:56:51.300
We look even now.
It won't be long.

565
00:56:51.500 --> 00:56:54.700
Find the child.
Find the child!

566
00:56:55.000 --> 00:56:57.500
Time is running out.

567
00:57:05.400 --> 00:57:07.800
- Good night.
- She is kinda cute.

568
00:57:09.700 --> 00:57:11.300
When she's quiet.

569
00:57:12.800 --> 00:57:14.600
She's really a princess.

570
00:57:14.800 --> 00:57:18.500
Really?
And you're a great sorcerer.

571
00:57:18.700 --> 00:57:20.600
And I'm the king of Kashmir.

572
00:57:21.800 --> 00:57:24.000
Go to sleep. Willow.

573
00:57:24.800 --> 00:57:27.100
Good night. Madmartigan.

574
00:57:27.400 --> 00:57:30.200
Rats! Big rats! Rats!

575
00:57:31.000 --> 00:57:32.900
Rats!

576
00:57:33.900 --> 00:57:38.500
Rool. you and
that stupid rat dream!

577
00:57:47.500 --> 00:57:50.100
<i>Tuatha...</i>

578
00:57:50.300 --> 00:57:52.300
<i>lawkathok...</i>

579
00:57:52.500 --> 00:57:54.300
<i>tuatha!</i>

580
00:58:03.800 --> 00:58:06.600
- There you are.
- Madmartigan!

581
00:58:08.200 --> 00:58:10.100
'Night. Willow.

582
00:58:22.300 --> 00:58:24.100
This way! This way!

583
00:58:36.100 --> 00:58:37.900
What are you doing?

584
00:58:38.100 --> 00:58:40.300
I found some black root.
She loves it!

585
00:58:40.600 --> 00:58:43.300
Black root?
I am the father of two children...

586
00:58:43.600 --> 00:58:45.400
and you never. ever
give a baby black root.

587
00:58:45.600 --> 00:58:48.600
My mother raised us
on black root.

588
00:58:48.900 --> 00:58:51.300
It's good for ya!
It puts hair on your chest.

589
00:58:51.500 --> 00:58:54.100
- Doesn't it. Sticks?
- Her name is not Sticks.

590
00:58:54.300 --> 00:58:57.000
She's Elora Danan.
the future empress of Tir Asleen.

591
00:58:57.400 --> 00:58:59.500
And the last thing she's gonna want
is a hairy chest!

592
00:59:04.100 --> 00:59:07.400
Did you see what he did?
He stole our black root.

593
00:59:07.800 --> 00:59:09.700
I'll get some more.
Don't worry about it.

594
00:59:14.100 --> 00:59:16.200
There it is! The island!

595
00:59:20.100 --> 00:59:22.800
We made it.

596
00:59:23.000 --> 00:59:25.900
We have led you to the island
of the sorceress Fin Raziel.

597
00:59:26.200 --> 00:59:29.100
- We'll get a boat in that village.
- A big boat.

598
00:59:48.600 --> 00:59:52.800
- Well. looks like I got you here.
- You? What did you do?

599
00:59:53.200 --> 00:59:56.000
All you did was hang around
and eat our eggs!

600
00:59:56.200 --> 00:59:59.500
- I found a boat. We're all set.
- Good.

601
00:59:59.700 --> 01:00:02.000
Take these two lizards out
and drown them.

602
01:00:02.200 --> 01:00:05.400
Lizards?
Who are you calling lizards?

603
01:00:07.700 --> 01:00:10.300
Your mother was a lizard!

604
01:00:13.400 --> 01:00:15.700
Goodbye. Sticks.

605
01:00:18.600 --> 01:00:21.300
If you really are a princess...

606
01:00:21.500 --> 01:00:23.500
take care of him.

607
01:00:31.500 --> 01:00:33.900
- Madmartigan!
- What?

608
01:00:35.100 --> 01:00:36.900
Thanks.

609
01:00:48.200 --> 01:00:51.400
- Keep walkin'. hero!
- Don't even turn around!

610
01:00:54.200 --> 01:00:56.500
It's all right. Elora.

611
01:00:56.700 --> 01:00:59.500
Go to sleep.
Nobody'll find you here.

612
01:00:59.800 --> 01:01:02.200
I'll be back with Fin Raziel
very soon.

613
01:01:02.400 --> 01:01:05.500
We will guard her
with our meagre lives.

614
01:01:34.100 --> 01:01:35.800
Raziel!

615
01:01:36.900 --> 01:01:40.600
Fin Raziel!
I have to talk to you. please!

616
01:01:52.500 --> 01:01:54.500
She's not here.

617
01:02:00.800 --> 01:02:04.200
Get back! Who are you?

618
01:02:05.500 --> 01:02:08.200
Who are you?

619
01:02:10.800 --> 01:02:13.600
- I'm Willow Ufgood.
- What are you doing here?

620
01:02:13.900 --> 01:02:17.300
I've come to find
the great sorceress Fin Raziel.

621
01:02:17.700 --> 01:02:20.100
That's me! I'm Raziel!

622
01:02:22.300 --> 01:02:24.100
This can't be right!

623
01:02:24.200 --> 01:02:27.500
One of Bavmorda's spells
transformed me.

624
01:02:30.100 --> 01:02:32.500
Believe me.
it could have been worse!

625
01:02:34.300 --> 01:02:38.400
Well. this wand is for you.
It's from Cherlindrea.

626
01:02:38.600 --> 01:02:40.700
Then the prophecy is true.

627
01:02:40.900 --> 01:02:44.200
The princess has been born.
Take me to her.

628
01:02:48.400 --> 01:02:51.500
It is Elora Danan.
Isn't she beautiful?

629
01:02:53.500 --> 01:02:56.300
Isn't she beautiful?

630
01:02:56.600 --> 01:02:59.200
- That's Raziel?
- I don't know.

631
01:02:59.500 --> 01:03:02.200
I expected something
more grand. Less...

632
01:03:02.400 --> 01:03:04.300
- Fuzzy.
- Fuzzy.

633
01:03:04.500 --> 01:03:08.100
You must use the wand.
Turn me back into my human form.

634
01:03:08.500 --> 01:03:11.600
- What do I do?
- You mean you're not a sorcerer?

635
01:03:13.000 --> 01:03:15.300
Yes. Sorta.

636
01:03:15.500 --> 01:03:16.800
I'm a farmer.

637
01:03:18.300 --> 01:03:20.800
- But I do know a few tricks.
- Tricks?

638
01:03:21.000 --> 01:03:25.300
Cherlindrea sent <i>you?</i>
You must learn real magic.

639
01:03:27.300 --> 01:03:29.500
- Horses!
- Horses!

640
01:03:29.700 --> 01:03:31.900
Quick! Take her! Hurry!

641
01:03:41.100 --> 01:03:43.900
I knew he was a traitor!

642
01:03:46.700 --> 01:03:49.100
- Sorry about this. peck.
- Keep your mouth shut.

643
01:03:50.600 --> 01:03:53.000
I told you we'd find them
without your help.

644
01:03:53.300 --> 01:03:55.100
- Give me that baby!
- No!

645
01:03:58.700 --> 01:04:02.400
- Give her back!
- Leave me alone! Don't touch me!

646
01:04:08.600 --> 01:04:10.300
This is the one
we're looking for.

647
01:04:10.600 --> 01:04:12.500
We must take it back
to Nockmaar.

648
01:04:16.800 --> 01:04:18.600
Lose your skirt?

649
01:04:26.800 --> 01:04:29.700
- I've still got what counts.
- Not for long.

650
01:04:36.500 --> 01:04:38.900
- Bring him.
- Over here!

651
01:04:57.700 --> 01:05:00.000
We'll never keep up
with those horses.

652
01:05:01.000 --> 01:05:03.900
- Then we will have to track them.
- That would take forever.

653
01:05:04.100 --> 01:05:06.600
Besides. even if we find them.
they'll catch us...

654
01:05:06.800 --> 01:05:09.800
stick us in cages. torture us
and finally devour us.

655
01:05:10.100 --> 01:05:11.900
Are you suggesting we go home?

656
01:05:12.100 --> 01:05:14.700
- Nah. This is more fun.
- All right.

657
01:05:15.000 --> 01:05:16.800
Fine. then.
Come on.

658
01:05:30.900 --> 01:05:34.100
I'm worried about Elora.
She doesn't sound good.

659
01:05:34.400 --> 01:05:36.900
Hurry! Practise
the chant I taught you!

660
01:05:38.200 --> 01:05:40.700
<i>Tanna looatha...</i>

661
01:05:40.900 --> 01:05:42.900
I can't remember
the middle part.

662
01:05:43.100 --> 01:05:45.000
<i>Locktwaar!</i>

663
01:05:45.200 --> 01:05:48.100
That's the word
that pleads for change.

664
01:05:48.300 --> 01:05:50.200
<i>Locktwaar.</i>

665
01:05:53.900 --> 01:05:56.800
Elora's cold and hungry.
She knows me.

666
01:05:57.200 --> 01:05:59.000
Please. let me take care of her.

667
01:05:59.100 --> 01:06:01.100
I don't need help from a peck.

668
01:06:05.800 --> 01:06:08.800
- What are you staring at?
- Your leg.

669
01:06:10.100 --> 01:06:12.000
I'd like to break it.

670
01:06:12.200 --> 01:06:14.100
You may find that difficult.
slave...

671
01:06:14.300 --> 01:06:16.400
while I'm up here
and you're down there.

672
01:06:19.600 --> 01:06:21.700
I hate that woman.

673
01:07:00.400 --> 01:07:02.300
I found it. Kael.

674
01:07:04.800 --> 01:07:07.100
That should make
my mother happy.

675
01:07:07.400 --> 01:07:09.200
What are they gonna do to her?

676
01:07:23.000 --> 01:07:25.500
<i>Hither walha...</i>

677
01:07:25.700 --> 01:07:29.000
<i>bairn deru bordak...</i>

678
01:07:29.300 --> 01:07:30.500
<i>bellanockt.</i>

679
01:07:32.200 --> 01:07:34.100
That's magic?
Smells terrible.

680
01:07:34.200 --> 01:07:37.200
- It's the life spark. It forms after...
- It stinks!

681
01:07:37.600 --> 01:07:40.600
- This whole thing stinks!
- Ignore him. Willow.

682
01:07:40.800 --> 01:07:43.700
- He's a fool!
- If only I had a sword!

683
01:07:45.000 --> 01:07:46.900
If only you'd quit
talking about it.

684
01:07:47.100 --> 01:07:50.300
Willow. you must transform me
to my human self.

685
01:07:50.500 --> 01:07:53.200
But. Raziel. I'm not ready yet.

686
01:07:53.400 --> 01:07:56.400
You'd better be.
Get me down.

687
01:08:00.300 --> 01:08:01.500
Ow!

688
01:08:05.300 --> 01:08:08.100
Why don't you help me get out of here
instead of chattering with that muskrat?

689
01:08:08.400 --> 01:08:09.500
Muskrat!

690
01:08:09.700 --> 01:08:14.100
When I change back to my former self.
I will crush this army...

691
01:08:14.500 --> 01:08:17.700
and take Elora Danan
to Tir Asleen...

692
01:08:18.000 --> 01:08:20.400
where she will be safe.

693
01:08:21.400 --> 01:08:24.800
Ow! What'd you bite me for?

694
01:08:25.100 --> 01:08:28.200
You need three drops of your blood
to put in the potion.

695
01:08:28.500 --> 01:08:30.100
You could've warned me.

696
01:08:31.900 --> 01:08:34.100
For beginners.
there's some pain...

697
01:08:34.400 --> 01:08:39.200
but don't let anything
break your concentration.

698
01:08:44.600 --> 01:08:47.300
<i>Hither greenan bairn</i>
<i>claideb lunanockt.</i>

699
01:08:47.500 --> 01:08:51.000
- Hello. everybody! We have arrived!
- You are saved.

700
01:08:52.200 --> 01:08:54.000
Don't interrupt.

701
01:08:55.700 --> 01:08:58.600
<i>Hither greenan bairn</i>
<i>claideb lunanockt.</i>

702
01:08:59.600 --> 01:09:01.500
What will you look like
if this works?

703
01:09:01.800 --> 01:09:04.100
- Don't interrupt.
- Sorry.

704
01:09:04.400 --> 01:09:06.100
<i>Hither greenan bairn</i>
<i>claideb lunanockt.</i>

705
01:09:06.400 --> 01:09:09.500
I am a young. beautiful woman.

706
01:09:09.800 --> 01:09:11.500
Concentrate. Willow.

707
01:09:11.600 --> 01:09:13.600
<i>Hither greenan bairn</i>
<i>claideb lunanockt.</i>

708
01:09:16.300 --> 01:09:18.300
You're losing me!

709
01:09:19.700 --> 01:09:21.900
<i>Hither greenan bairn</i>
<i>claideb lunanockt.</i>

710
01:09:27.600 --> 01:09:29.700
You all right?
Nice try. Willow.

711
01:09:38.000 --> 01:09:41.700
Farmers!
Cherlindrea sends me farmers!

712
01:09:43.100 --> 01:09:45.400
The Nelwyn
really butchered that one.

713
01:09:45.600 --> 01:09:47.400
I'm sorry. Raziel.

714
01:09:47.700 --> 01:09:49.100
You want out?

715
01:09:49.300 --> 01:09:51.800
Easy. We can pick a lock.
Come on.

716
01:09:52.000 --> 01:09:53.600
No. No. no.
Like this!

717
01:09:53.900 --> 01:09:55.800
I know what I'm doing.
It's my spear. Leave it alone.

718
01:09:55.900 --> 01:09:58.200
Let me do it.

719
01:09:58.400 --> 01:10:00.200
Out of the way. rodents.

720
01:10:01.600 --> 01:10:02.700
Take your hand off that.

721
01:10:02.800 --> 01:10:07.000
You leave that alone.
you stupid. fat Daikini!

722
01:10:09.900 --> 01:10:12.200
Dust of broken hearts.

723
01:10:23.700 --> 01:10:25.300
You are free!

724
01:10:25.600 --> 01:10:26.600
Come on. Madmartigan.

725
01:10:26.800 --> 01:10:28.900
Let's get Elora Danan
out of here.

726
01:10:29.200 --> 01:10:30.900
Yeah.

727
01:10:31.200 --> 01:10:33.200
- It'll be fun.
- Come on.

728
01:10:45.600 --> 01:10:47.500
- Are you all right?
- Yeah.

729
01:10:49.100 --> 01:10:51.100
I feel good.

730
01:10:51.300 --> 01:10:53.200
The dust of broken hearts.

731
01:10:55.000 --> 01:10:56.300
Come on!

732
01:11:03.000 --> 01:11:05.900
- Let me see!
- Let <i>me</i> see. You always see.

733
01:11:06.100 --> 01:11:08.400
There's Elora. right there.
on those furs.

734
01:11:11.000 --> 01:11:14.300
Hey. wait! Leave this to us.
It's too dangerous for you.

735
01:11:14.700 --> 01:11:18.700
Only one of us should go in there.
I know what I'm doing.

736
01:11:49.800 --> 01:11:52.300
Wait. No. no!

737
01:12:03.600 --> 01:12:06.300
- I love you.
- Madmartigan!

738
01:12:06.500 --> 01:12:09.300
What are you doing?
Get the baby!

739
01:12:09.600 --> 01:12:10.800
Come on!

740
01:12:26.400 --> 01:12:28.400
Wake from this hateful sleep.

741
01:12:28.600 --> 01:12:30.800
It deprives me of your beauty.

742
01:12:32.300 --> 01:12:35.600
- The beauty of your eyes...
- One move. jackass...

743
01:12:35.900 --> 01:12:38.600
and you really will be a woman.

744
01:12:38.800 --> 01:12:44.300
You are my sun! My moon!
My starlit sky.

745
01:12:44.800 --> 01:12:48.300
Without you. I dwell in darkness.
I love you.

746
01:12:50.000 --> 01:12:51.400
What are you doing here?

747
01:12:51.500 --> 01:12:54.700
Your power has enchanted me.
I stand helpless against it.

748
01:12:55.000 --> 01:12:56.800
Come to me now.

749
01:12:57.000 --> 01:12:59.300
Tonight. let me worship you
in my arms.

750
01:12:59.600 --> 01:13:02.100
- Get away from me!
- I love you!

751
01:13:02.400 --> 01:13:04.700
Stop saying that!

752
01:13:04.900 --> 01:13:08.900
How can I stop the beating of my heart?
It pounds like never before.

753
01:13:09.300 --> 01:13:11.700
- Out of fear.
- Out of love!

754
01:13:11.900 --> 01:13:14.300
I can stop it.
I'll kill you.

755
01:13:14.500 --> 01:13:16.400
Death. next to love.
is a trivial thing.

756
01:13:20.200 --> 01:13:22.500
Your touch is worth 100.000 deaths.

757
01:13:27.600 --> 01:13:29.000
What goes on here?

758
01:13:34.300 --> 01:13:36.100
Deceiver!

759
01:13:37.800 --> 01:13:39.500
Stop him!

760
01:13:48.700 --> 01:13:51.100
Get me out!

761
01:14:01.700 --> 01:14:03.600
You <i>are</i> great!

762
01:14:06.800 --> 01:14:08.400
Get on that shield!

763
01:14:25.900 --> 01:14:27.700
After them!

764
01:14:41.200 --> 01:14:42.500
They're getting away!

765
01:14:52.000 --> 01:14:54.000
- Follow me. Rool.
- Where are you?

766
01:14:54.300 --> 01:14:55.900
I don't know.

767
01:14:57.100 --> 01:14:59.000
Oh. no!
Where did everybody go?

768
01:14:59.200 --> 01:15:01.100
Maybe it was something we said.

769
01:16:40.900 --> 01:16:42.700
What the hell happened up there?

770
01:16:43.000 --> 01:16:44.900
You started spouting poetry.

771
01:16:45.100 --> 01:16:47.600
- Poetry?
- Yeah.

772
01:16:47.800 --> 01:16:50.700
"I love you. Sorsha.
I worship you. Sorsha."

773
01:16:51.000 --> 01:16:52.900
You almost got us killed!

774
01:16:53.100 --> 01:16:54.900
"I love you. Sorsha"?

775
01:16:55.100 --> 01:16:57.400
I don't love her.
She kicked me in the face.

776
01:16:57.600 --> 01:17:00.000
I hate her! Don't I?

777
01:17:03.200 --> 01:17:05.500
Kael! Kael!

778
01:17:05.700 --> 01:17:07.200
Nockmaar soldiers!

779
01:17:10.400 --> 01:17:12.400
Hide! Get the children!
Come on!

780
01:17:15.500 --> 01:17:17.800
- Hide! Get the children!
- They're after us!

781
01:17:18.000 --> 01:17:21.500
- We need a place to hide.
- Come on. Follow me. Quick!

782
01:17:38.300 --> 01:17:40.900
I knew you'd get out
of that rattrap.

783
01:17:43.500 --> 01:17:45.400
You left me to die. Airk.

784
01:17:45.600 --> 01:17:48.700
I probably saved your life.
We were slaughtered. and I lost a lot...

785
01:17:48.900 --> 01:17:49.800
Quiet!

786
01:17:52.500 --> 01:17:54.200
Tear this village apart!

787
01:17:55.100 --> 01:17:57.300
Look everywhere!

788
01:17:57.600 --> 01:17:58.700
Find the child!

789
01:18:34.600 --> 01:18:37.500
Tell Sorsha
I search the north bank!

790
01:18:37.700 --> 01:18:38.800
Yes. General.

791
01:18:52.700 --> 01:18:54.600
Quiet!

792
01:19:14.200 --> 01:19:17.000
- Sorsha!
- Back.

793
01:19:17.800 --> 01:19:18.900
Back!

794
01:19:25.700 --> 01:19:26.900
Back.

795
01:19:28.800 --> 01:19:31.600
- Keep the baby quiet.
- She needs to be changed.

796
01:19:32.600 --> 01:19:34.400
- Nockmaar scum!
- You'll never defeat us.

797
01:19:34.500 --> 01:19:36.100
- Give up the baby!
- Shut up!

798
01:19:38.300 --> 01:19:41.600
- Why does Bavmorda want this baby?
- She's a princess.

799
01:19:41.900 --> 01:19:44.400
- We're taking her to Tir Asleen.
- Tir Asleen?

800
01:19:44.700 --> 01:19:46.600
Even if you could find it. peck...

801
01:19:46.700 --> 01:19:49.000
she's right... you'd never
get past the Nockmaar army.

802
01:19:49.200 --> 01:19:52.900
There's an even bigger army
at Tir Asleen. if we can get there.

803
01:19:57.700 --> 01:20:00.300
I've lost more than half my men
fighting Bavmorda.

804
01:20:00.500 --> 01:20:02.400
Now you and this peck
are gonna take her on?

805
01:20:03.600 --> 01:20:06.200
You always told me you served
no one. Madmartigan.

806
01:20:06.500 --> 01:20:08.300
Since when are you a crusader?

807
01:20:10.700 --> 01:20:12.700
He's not gonna help you. peck.

808
01:20:14.100 --> 01:20:16.300
He's a worthless thief.

809
01:20:17.500 --> 01:20:19.800
I'm not a thief. Airk.

810
01:20:20.000 --> 01:20:21.500
He's not a thief.

811
01:20:24.200 --> 01:20:25.200
Are you?

812
01:20:39.800 --> 01:20:42.100
I serve the Nelwyn. Airk.

813
01:20:48.400 --> 01:20:50.800
- Want to come with us?
- You'll never make it.

814
01:20:52.900 --> 01:20:55.100
Then once again
we say goodbye.

815
01:21:08.700 --> 01:21:11.900
- Over here!
- Sorsha!

816
01:21:12.100 --> 01:21:14.300
Weapons down or she's dead!

817
01:21:29.000 --> 01:21:30.800
Get to your horses!
After them!

818
01:22:17.200 --> 01:22:19.500
This way!
This way!

819
01:22:19.800 --> 01:22:22.300
As the crow flies. you fools!

820
01:22:29.400 --> 01:22:32.000
- You're holding me too tight!
- I don't want you to get away.

821
01:22:32.300 --> 01:22:36.100
Why? Because I'm your sun.
your moon. your starlit sky?

822
01:22:38.700 --> 01:22:40.700
Get your hair out of my face
or I'll chop it off.

823
01:22:44.800 --> 01:22:46.400
Did I really...

824
01:22:46.600 --> 01:22:48.600
Did I really say
those things last night?

825
01:22:48.800 --> 01:22:51.700
- In your tent?
- You said you loved me.

826
01:22:52.000 --> 01:22:54.300
- I don't remember that.
- You lied to me!

827
01:22:54.600 --> 01:22:55.700
No. I...

828
01:22:57.000 --> 01:22:59.300
I just wasn't myself last night.

829
01:22:59.500 --> 01:23:03.000
I suppose my power enchanted you
and you were helpless against it.

830
01:23:04.500 --> 01:23:06.500
- Sort of.
- Then what?

831
01:23:07.900 --> 01:23:11.000
- It went away.
- Went away?

832
01:23:11.300 --> 01:23:14.000
"I dwell in darkness without you."
and it went away?

833
01:23:14.300 --> 01:23:15.900
Yeah.

834
01:23:37.600 --> 01:23:39.400
Hurry! Kael's coming!

835
01:23:44.100 --> 01:23:46.200
Madmartigan. come on! Now!

836
01:23:54.400 --> 01:23:56.100
Madmartigan. come on!

837
01:23:58.000 --> 01:24:00.600
They're coming! Away!

838
01:24:00.900 --> 01:24:02.000
Go on!

839
01:24:20.200 --> 01:24:21.600
Whoa! Whoa!

840
01:24:23.400 --> 01:24:24.800
This way!

841
01:24:31.100 --> 01:24:34.700
Tir Asleen!
At last. Tir Asleen!

842
01:24:45.800 --> 01:24:47.100
Hello?

843
01:24:49.100 --> 01:24:50.500
Hello?

844
01:24:54.800 --> 01:24:56.100
Hello?

845
01:24:58.100 --> 01:25:00.600
Why did I listen to you. peck?

846
01:25:00.800 --> 01:25:04.100
"Everything will be all right
once we get to Tir Asleen."

847
01:25:05.200 --> 01:25:07.900
The only army around is the one that's
about to ride across this valley...

848
01:25:08.200 --> 01:25:09.900
and wipe us out!

849
01:25:10.200 --> 01:25:13.000
But Cherlindrea said
we'd be safe here.

850
01:25:13.900 --> 01:25:16.800
Safe? Look at these people.

851
01:25:17.100 --> 01:25:20.800
This place is cursed. peck.
It's falling apart. Open your eyes!

852
01:25:21.100 --> 01:25:22.300
And it...

853
01:25:24.800 --> 01:25:26.700
Trolls.

854
01:25:29.900 --> 01:25:31.800
I hate trolls.

855
01:25:32.700 --> 01:25:35.000
This is the work of Bavmorda.

856
01:25:44.300 --> 01:25:46.700
Willow? The wand.

857
01:25:47.000 --> 01:25:50.200
- Turn me back into my human form.
- Are you sure?

858
01:26:08.600 --> 01:26:09.700
Good.

859
01:26:17.300 --> 01:26:19.200
Hurry. Willow.
Transform me.

860
01:26:19.400 --> 01:26:22.200
I can't do it.
I'm just not a sorcerer.

861
01:26:22.500 --> 01:26:28.000
But you can be.
Speak and be one with the words.

862
01:26:28.500 --> 01:26:31.500
<i>Avalorium greenan...</i>

863
01:26:32.100 --> 01:26:34.800
<i>luatha tye...</i>

864
01:26:35.200 --> 01:26:37.800
Oh. Willow. you're losing me.

865
01:26:42.200 --> 01:26:44.300
Madmartigan. Kael's coming!

866
01:26:44.500 --> 01:26:48.600
- Willow. you idiot.
- Raziel?

867
01:26:49.800 --> 01:26:52.200
Arm that catapult up there.

868
01:27:14.000 --> 01:27:17.500
Good work. Madmartigan.

869
01:27:17.800 --> 01:27:19.300
What happened to you?

870
01:27:19.600 --> 01:27:22.000
Assault!
Sorsha. battering ram!

871
01:27:27.400 --> 01:27:28.700
Cut it down!

872
01:27:40.900 --> 01:27:41.900
Faster!

873
01:27:57.400 --> 01:27:59.600
Forward! Break it down!

874
01:28:20.400 --> 01:28:22.700
Again! Again!

875
01:28:27.500 --> 01:28:29.800
Willow. use the wand
on that troll.

876
01:28:32.300 --> 01:28:33.600
<i>Bellalockt!</i>

877
01:28:56.800 --> 01:29:00.100
Break it down! Forward!

878
01:29:47.400 --> 01:29:49.700
Get him!

879
01:30:11.700 --> 01:30:13.200
The other side!

880
01:30:28.000 --> 01:30:30.100
Destroy the beast!
Find the baby!

881
01:30:31.300 --> 01:30:32.900
Take that!

882
01:32:09.100 --> 01:32:11.700
Madmartigan. help!

883
01:32:23.200 --> 01:32:24.900
Get him. Madmartigan!

884
01:32:35.300 --> 01:32:36.700
Here.

885
01:32:53.400 --> 01:32:54.600
The baby!

886
01:33:56.500 --> 01:33:59.500
Airk's army. Get Kael!

887
01:33:59.800 --> 01:34:02.000
Airk's army!

888
01:34:04.700 --> 01:34:06.700
- We are here!
- You are rescued!

889
01:34:06.900 --> 01:34:09.700
- Charge!
- Charge!

890
01:34:26.800 --> 01:34:29.000
No mercy!

891
01:34:42.600 --> 01:34:44.300
Elora!

892
01:34:45.800 --> 01:34:46.900
Willow!

893
01:34:53.400 --> 01:34:55.200
- Elora's gone.
- Willow.

894
01:34:56.500 --> 01:34:59.300
They've taken her.
There were too many of them.

895
01:35:04.800 --> 01:35:06.600
Can you ride?

896
01:35:10.100 --> 01:35:11.500
Let's ride.

897
01:35:23.900 --> 01:35:26.200
I have the child!

898
01:35:50.800 --> 01:35:52.700
We need towers
and a battering ram!

899
01:35:53.000 --> 01:35:55.900
Break out the tents!
Make camp!

900
01:35:56.200 --> 01:35:58.100
Make camp!

901
01:35:58.300 --> 01:36:00.000
We'll assault at first light.

902
01:36:14.000 --> 01:36:15.900
Where's Sorsha?

903
01:36:17.200 --> 01:36:19.800
She has turned against us.
Your Highness.

904
01:36:24.100 --> 01:36:26.400
Turned against me?

905
01:36:30.100 --> 01:36:32.100
Prepare for the ritual!

906
01:36:55.900 --> 01:36:58.000
This is not an army.

907
01:37:01.400 --> 01:37:03.900
Quick. Hide.

908
01:37:08.800 --> 01:37:11.700
Use the shelter chant.
Protect yourself.

909
01:37:12.000 --> 01:37:13.800
- Why?
- Just do it.

910
01:37:19.700 --> 01:37:23.900
- We've come for Elora Danan.
- You dare to challenge me?

911
01:37:24.200 --> 01:37:26.300
You're not warriors.

912
01:37:28.100 --> 01:37:29.400
You're pigs!

913
01:37:45.300 --> 01:37:47.000
You're all pigs!

914
01:37:49.200 --> 01:37:50.300
Pigs!

915
01:37:56.900 --> 01:37:59.700
<i>Avaggdu luatha bairn</i>
<i>off haefermore.</i>

916
01:38:08.700 --> 01:38:10.700
Sorsha!

917
01:38:11.900 --> 01:38:13.300
Mother. no!

918
01:38:16.500 --> 01:38:17.700
<i>Kothon!</i>

919
01:38:39.300 --> 01:38:42.700
<i>Avaggdu luatha bairn</i>
<i>off haefermore.</i>

920
01:38:57.600 --> 01:38:59.200
Begin the ritual.

921
01:38:59.300 --> 01:39:02.000
This baby will not destroy me.

922
01:39:06.700 --> 01:39:08.200
Come. thunder!

923
01:39:10.500 --> 01:39:12.300
Come. lightning!

924
01:39:13.200 --> 01:39:16.700
Touch this altar
with your powers.

925
01:39:40.200 --> 01:39:43.300
We've come all this way
and now Elora Danan's gonna die!

926
01:39:43.600 --> 01:39:46.300
No. we can still defeat Bavmorda.

927
01:39:46.600 --> 01:39:48.600
She's too powerful. Raziel.

928
01:39:48.800 --> 01:39:51.800
Transform me.
and I will destroy her.

929
01:39:57.300 --> 01:40:00.900
Elements of eternity.
above and below.

930
01:40:02.100 --> 01:40:05.700
Balance of essence.
fire beget snow.

931
01:40:07.400 --> 01:40:10.400
- <i>Locktwarr danalora luatha danu...</i>
- Willow...

932
01:40:10.700 --> 01:40:12.600
- believe in the words.
- <i>tuatha. tuatha...</i>

933
01:40:12.900 --> 01:40:14.900
- Concentrate.
- <i>chnox danu.</i>

934
01:40:15.100 --> 01:40:16.600
<i>Locktwarr danalora...</i>

935
01:40:16.900 --> 01:40:20.600
- <i>luatha danu tuatha. tuatha.</i>
- Oh. no!

936
01:40:28.000 --> 01:40:33.000
Don't give up. Willow!

937
01:41:14.400 --> 01:41:18.100
- Has it been so long?
- I'm sorry.

938
01:41:20.600 --> 01:41:23.900
Willow. we have work to do.

939
01:41:25.400 --> 01:41:27.000
Give me the wand.

940
01:41:27.900 --> 01:41:31.200
We must undo Bavmorda's sorcery.

941
01:41:34.300 --> 01:41:36.200
Let them in now.

942
01:41:41.100 --> 01:41:44.300
<i>Tuatha grin chnox</i>
<i>y foel famau.</i>

943
01:41:58.600 --> 01:42:01.600
Black fires
forever kindled within...

944
01:42:01.800 --> 01:42:04.000
let the second rite begin.

945
01:42:21.900 --> 01:42:22.900
Quick. inside.

946
01:42:23.900 --> 01:42:26.300
That won't breach the wall.
We can't get inside.

947
01:42:26.500 --> 01:42:29.300
- Elora Danan will die...
- Unless we save her.

948
01:42:29.500 --> 01:42:31.800
- Bavmorda's too powerful.
- No!

949
01:42:32.900 --> 01:42:37.200
She cannot transform you again.
My spell is protecting this camp.

950
01:42:37.600 --> 01:42:39.500
But can your magic
get us inside the fortress?

951
01:42:41.900 --> 01:42:43.600
We can't do it.

952
01:42:43.700 --> 01:42:45.200
Wait!

953
01:42:45.500 --> 01:42:48.400
Back home in my village.
we have a lot of gophers.

954
01:42:48.600 --> 01:42:50.800
- Willow. this is war. not agriculture.
- I know.

955
01:42:51.100 --> 01:42:54.000
But I have an idea
how to get inside the castle.

956
01:42:58.800 --> 01:43:01.700
<i>Ocht veth bordak stira.</i>

957
01:43:02.000 --> 01:43:04.500
<i>Ocht veth bordak stira.</i>

958
01:43:12.900 --> 01:43:15.800
Madmartigan. you and I are soldiers.
The peck's plan will never work.

959
01:43:17.600 --> 01:43:20.600
If the baby dies.
all hope for the future is lost.

960
01:43:23.200 --> 01:43:24.900
I'm going to fight.

961
01:43:28.600 --> 01:43:30.300
Me too.

962
01:43:37.700 --> 01:43:40.500
All right. we've got to decide
who's gonna go and who's gonna stay.

963
01:44:30.800 --> 01:44:35.400
Willow. all these years
I have waited to face Bavmorda.

964
01:44:35.800 --> 01:44:38.200
It is you
that has made this possible.

965
01:44:39.700 --> 01:44:43.700
Whatever happens.
I shall always admire you.

966
01:44:54.600 --> 01:44:56.800
Your children...

967
01:44:57.000 --> 01:44:59.600
will come to remember this day.

968
01:45:10.200 --> 01:45:13.100
We call upon you to surrender!

969
01:45:15.400 --> 01:45:17.200
We are all-powerful sorcerers.

970
01:45:18.500 --> 01:45:21.800
Give us the baby.
or we'll destroy you!

971
01:45:28.300 --> 01:45:30.600
Kill them!

972
01:45:50.000 --> 01:45:51.600
Patience. Willow.

973
01:45:53.500 --> 01:45:55.100
Courage. Willow.

974
01:46:11.300 --> 01:46:13.200
Back to the castle!

975
01:46:39.000 --> 01:46:42.100
<i>Ocht veth nockthirth bordak!</i>

976
01:46:42.300 --> 01:46:46.000
Exile the child to the 13th night.

977
01:46:54.000 --> 01:46:55.300
This way!

978
01:47:34.700 --> 01:47:40.700
<i>Nockthirth</i>
<i>plankton firth foreth forewar.</i>

979
01:47:41.100 --> 01:47:43.300
<i>Ocht veth nock!</i>

980
01:47:43.500 --> 01:47:45.900
It's all right. Willow.

981
01:47:46.100 --> 01:47:47.900
You don't have to go.

982
01:47:48.200 --> 01:47:50.800
Light the 13th candle!

983
01:48:05.900 --> 01:48:07.600
Raziel.

984
01:48:07.800 --> 01:48:09.100
Mother!

985
01:48:13.300 --> 01:48:17.500
Traitor child.
I must despise you now.

986
01:48:48.300 --> 01:48:51.100
- I won't let you kill that child.
- Away!

987
01:48:51.400 --> 01:48:52.700
<i>Avaggdu...</i>

988
01:48:53.700 --> 01:48:56.200
<i>strokt!</i>

989
01:49:12.800 --> 01:49:16.100
Your powers have gained
in strength. Raziel.

990
01:49:16.400 --> 01:49:21.300
I have Cherlindrea's wand.
Bavmorda.

991
01:49:23.800 --> 01:49:27.600
Elora Danan will be queen.

992
01:49:40.800 --> 01:49:41.900
Now you die!

993
01:49:46.400 --> 01:49:49.300
<i>Furrochk flarem!</i>

994
01:50:19.500 --> 01:50:21.700
<i>Claideb cla...</i>

995
01:50:23.500 --> 01:50:26.800
<i>Clai main!</i>
<i>Lunano ockht!</i>

996
01:50:29.000 --> 01:50:31.700
<i>Bachktu inno!</i>

997
01:52:23.700 --> 01:52:24.700
Airk!

998
01:52:28.100 --> 01:52:29.900
Win this war for me.

999
01:53:08.900 --> 01:53:10.400
Die!

1000
01:55:10.100 --> 01:55:12.900
Bring back that child. peck.

1001
01:55:17.300 --> 01:55:18.500
Who are you?

1002
01:55:22.400 --> 01:55:24.300
